ieces tagged with rule-stack provenance, ablation tooling documented for operators, review log template in place. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-033** [T2] Migrate Anthony's existing recorded music + handpicked field recordings into `samples/library/` with appropriate metadata. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~18 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~6 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ---\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ## Requirements Coverage\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **MUST requirements:** 37/37 covered\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **SHOULD requirements:** 3 included as stretch\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **MUST requirements:** 32/32 covered\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **SHOULD requirements:** 1 included as stretch\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **✓ All MUST requirements covered.**\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndiff --git a/sdp/task-graph.md b/sdp/task-graph.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nindex 541f6b7..f7cc1bc 100644\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n--- a/sdp/task-graph.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+++ b/sdp/task-graph.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -1,8 +1,8 @@\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-# PRD: CypherClaw Humanization — Structured Expression Rendering Layer — Task Graph\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+# PRD: CypherClaw Sampler — Granular Memory Voice as Primary Instrument — Task Graph\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Generated:** 2026-04-16T18:19:25.335643+00:00\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Total tasks:** 40\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Estimated effort:** ~129 hours\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Generated:** 2026-04-25T18:39:59.551260+00:00\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Total tasks:** 33\\\\\\\\