ition variance. | T1 | 4 | 3 | CCH-028 | T-011 | - arc_shape selected from PerformanceIntent or, if unspecified, sampled from authored distribution weighted by intent_tag<br/>- for intent_tag=withhold, occasional flat arc (tempo_deviation_pct=0) is expressive<br/>- tests verify shape distribution over many phrases and flat-arc presence for withhold intent |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| 28 | T-028 | Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. | T1 | 4 | 3 | CCH-029 | T-011 | - PerformanceIntent.restraint ∈ [0, 1] scales: tempo_deviation_pct (× (1-restraint)), dynamic_range_db (× (1-restraint·0.7)), silence-budget thresholds (× (1 + restraint))<br/>- R2, R10 read restraint at runtime<br/>- tests verify restraint=0 is neutral and restraint=1 produces near-flat phrases with extended silence |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Sprint 3 total:** ~30 hrs\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 14 | T-014 | Add systemd unit `cypherclaw-sample-capture.service` that runs `sample_capture_daemon.py` with `Restart=always`, dependent on `cypherclaw-jack.service`. | T2 | 3 | 6 | CCS-020 | T-011 | - unit file at `my-claw/systemd/cypherclaw-sample-capture.service`<br/>- `User=user`, `LimitMEMLOCK=infinity`, `ExecStart=/home/user/cypherclaw/.venv/bin/python3 /home/user/cypherclaw/tools/sample_capture_daemon.py`<br/>- `After=cypherclaw-jack.service`, `Requires=cypherclaw-jack.service`<br/>- enabled on boot via `cypherclaw_boot.sh`<br/>- daemon survives a 30-minute soak test with simulated JACK xruns |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 15 | T-015 | Implement TDD-grade test fixtures with canned 1-second audio windows representing each detector branch (silence, footsteps, dishwasher, music, dogs, transient cluster) for fast deterministic CI. | T1 | 4 | 3 | CCS-021 | T-011 | - `my-claw/tests/fixtures/sample_capture/` directory with WAV fixtures<br/>- `test_sample_capture_daemon.py` exercises each fixture against the detector